name: Konitz Snuggle Mugs Tea Collage
description:
Any time can be tea time. Enjoy your daily tea ritual with the Tea Collage Snuggle Mugs. Contemporary tea leaf graphics against black print make this set a must-have for your favorite, freshly-brewed teas.
At Konitz everything revolves around mugs. Konitz offers a wide assortment of coffee and tea mugs, as well as espresso, cappuccino and cafe-au-lait cups with flower, animal, artistic, modern and trendy decors. Konitz is constantly on the look-out for the newest and most "in" trends in the area of fashion, design, technology and living, in order to create new mugs. Headquartered in Germany, and founded by the Rosenthal family that created Rosenthal Porcelain, Konitz mugs and tea cups are in a category all by themselves.
Microwave and dishwasher safe

description: These thick walled Santa Fe-style mugs in blue with a speckled glaze are reminiscent of enameled cookware. With a 15-ounce capacity and wide bowl these mugs are perfect for tea, coffee, or even soup.

name: Bistro Double-Wall Insulated Glass Espresso Mug
description:
Enjoy your favorite drink using the Bodum 10602-10 Bistro Double-Wall Insulated Glass Espresso Mugs (Set of 2). Made of glass , this espresso mugs is just what you need for a delicious drink any time of the day. This set of 2 double-wall glass espresso shot mugs each have a 4.7-ounce capacity. With a mouth-blown, lab-quality borosilicate glass construction, these mugs are durable and heat resistant. A 2-layer design creates dramatic optical illusion and prevents condensation. Safe for dishwasher and microwave use; not for use with metal utensils. Winner of prestigious European IF Design Award. When form follows function, design just works. Abiding by this belief, the Bistro Double Wall Glass Line serves best if used to keep ice cold drinks cold and hot drinks hot. The Bistro family of mugs is streamlined: shaped without many edges and corners, employing a form for everyday use with the special double wall glass thermal effect. The Bistro line is made of mouth-blown borosilicate glass known for its amazing insulating qualities. It is a perfect glass line for people enjoying a whole range of beverages, from ice cold drinks to espresso or cafe latte.

Product Features: Microwave Safe

name: Hobnail Highball Glass
description:
Serve your favorite drinks in style with these artful highball glasses. A classic hobnail pattern lends a whimsical touch to these tall glasses while providing a pleasant texture for a better grip. Choose from a variety of colorful options to complement your decor, or select clear for highlighting the glass's contents to show your mastery at the bar.

Constructed from 100 percent glass, these highball glasses have a solid, quality feel for serving guests or using at family meals. Use this set of six glasses to serve iced tea to a crowd on the patio or to drink milk at dinner during a family meal. Smooth interiors wash up easily, while the patterned exteriors reduce the risk of spills.

Color options include clear, kiwi, pink and purple
Constructed from 100 percent glass for a solid feel
Six glasses per set
Hobnail highball glass for indoor use

description:

Bring a set of these Libbey cooler glasses home to provide enough drinkware for the entire family, in a size that accommodates larger drinks with plenty of ice. Replace mismatched glasses in your own kitchen, or give these high-quality cooler glasses as a gift to a family just beginning to outfit their kitchen.

description:
These Counterpart flexible cutting mats come packed in a set of four assorted solid bright colors and food icons in the corners of each, making it easy to utilize the appropriate mat for raw foods, thus avoiding cross-contamination. These terrific mats are flexible so you can roll up to create a funnel-like exit for the transfer of foods to the pan without spilling. These flex mats include micro ban protection, the most trusted anti-microbial product protection in the world, that features built-in defense properties that inhibit the growth of stain- and odor-causing bacteria, mold and mildew, thus always at work to keep the mats bacteria-free between cleanings. name: Cuisinart CPT-180 Stainless Steel 4-slice Toaster
description:
Toast bread, bagels, English muffins and Kaiser rolls perfectly every time with this Cuisinart stainless steel four-slice toaster. The perfect marriage of retro styling and superior functionality, this sleek toaster is ideal for people short on counter space but long on love for baked goods. Durable and high-quality stainless steel construction ensures that this toaster is around for years of daily use.

Defrost your bread straight from the freezer in this convenient toaster, and use the warm feature if you need a bit more time to get the butter onto your bread. A motorized lift allows you to raise and lower your bread with the push of a button, and the cord wraps under the toaster to help you keep your counters tidy.

Silver four-slice toaster features six settings to get the perfect amount of bake on each item you warm
Stainless steel construction is durable and attractive

Measures 7"H x 11"W x 10"D

name: Hamilton Beach 24810 Keep Warm 4-slice Long Slot Toaster
description:
Complete your kitchen with the addition of this convenienent Hamilton Beach 24810 Keep Warm 4-slice Long Slot Toaster. Tired of cold toast. The Hamilton Beach keep warm 4 slice long slot toaster keeps your toast warm without over toasting. Three beeps sound when the toast cycle is complete, and keep warm mode holds the food in the slot where it stays warm for up to three minutes before automatically shutting off. This toaster features two extra-wide long slots, illuminated easy-push buttons, a defrost function, and shade selector dial. Wider slots allow you to uniformly toast and warm bagels, english muffins, and artisan breads. Toast to your liking with the shade selector offering seven different settings, and quickly stop any toasting with the cancel button. Frozen foods are perfectly toasted by using the defrost button. You won't have to reach into the hot toaster slot to retrieve smaller slices of bread. This toaster has a toast boost feature to lift the bread up higher for easy removal. A slide out crumb tray offers fast cleanup and an under-base cord wrap keeps things tidy when not in use.

easily fits artisan breads and bagels
